cs.CR, cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.LG, cs.AI 

This paper deals with the problem of deobfuscation, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also heavily relies on machine learning techniques (cs.LG) and binary analysis (cs.PL), as well as software engineering principles (cs.SE) for developing a static and generic evaluation technique. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of hybrid symbolic analysis and machine learning techniques (cs.AI) for deobfuscation.
